                <li>**Strategy Call:** We schedule a brief call to align on the narrative and commercial goals.</li>
                <li>**Proposal:** If we proceed, the **$50 fee is credited toward the final proposal**, which includes the estimated cost and timeline for the full custom lyric.</li>
